OL,3,CSea swimmer to sue South West Water
OL,4,Cfor dumping sewage
OL,6,FA sea swimmer from Exmouth is hoping
OL,7,Fto become one of the first people to
OL,8,Fever successfully sue a water company
OL,9,Ffor dumping sewage in the sea.
OL,11,FJo Bateman has decided to challenge
OL,12,FSouth West Water (SWW) in the courts
OL,13,Fafter losing more than 120 days of sea
OL,14,Fswims to sewage discharges.
