OL,3,CSea swimmer to sue South West Water
OL,4,Cfor dumping sewage
OL,6,FJo said: "Last year because of the
OL,7,Fspills, because I won't swim for 48
OL,8,Fhours after a spill - because that's
OL,9,Fthe World Health Organisation's advice
OL,10,F- there were over 120 days when I was
OL,11,Funable to swim, that's a third of a
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,F"It's absolutely atrocious, it's
OL,15,Fdisgusting and I don't know how
OL,16,Fthey've been able to get away with it
OL,17,Ffor so long", she added.
OL,19,FDischarging raw sewage into the sea
OL,20,Fafter heavy rain is legal for water
OL,21,Fcompanies.
