OL,3,CSea swimmer to sue South West Water
OL,4,Cfor dumping sewage
OL,6,FBut Jo feels because of the number of
OL,7,Fdays water companies claim this is
OL,8,Fnecessary, she has decided to withhold
OL,9,Fher sewerage charge and says companies
OL,10,Flike SWW should have been investing in
OL,11,Ftheir services more.
OL,13,FJo said: "There's not really any
OL,14,Fexcuse for it ever, because if they
OL,15,Fhad been investing in the
OL,16,Finfrastructure for the last 10-20-30
OL,17,Fyears, keeping on top of it, adding
OL,18,Fwhat was needed when we added new
OL,19,Fhouses, maintaining what's there, we
OL,20,Fwouldn't be in this mess now."
