OL,3,CSea swimmer to sue South West Water
OL,4,Cfor dumping sewage
OL,6,FIn response to Jo's criticism, SWW
OL,7,Fsaid it is currently investing #850m
OL,8,Fthis financial year, with one priority
OL,9,Fto reduce overflows at more than 150
OL,10,Ffifty bathing and shellfish areas.
OL,12,FJohn Halsall, the chief operating
OL,13,Fofficer of SWW, said in a statement:
OL,14,F"Like all our customers, including Ms
OL,15,FBateman, we care deeply about the
OL,16,Fquality of our region's bathing
OL,17,Fwaters. It's always upsetting if
OL,18,Fanyone feels they can't enjoy the
OL,19,Fbeach when they want to.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
