OL,3,CSea swimmer to sue South West Water
OL,4,Cfor dumping sewage
OL,6,F"Our customers rightly want us to
OL,7,Freduce the use of storm overflows
OL,8,Fwhich are an essential pressure
OL,9,Frelease valve that prevents flooding
OL,10,Fto homes and businesses. We have a
OL,11,Fplan and it is working, but we know
OL,12,Fthere is more to do. This is our top
OL,13,Fpriority."
OL,15,FThe company intends to invest #38m in
OL,16,FExmouth by 2030.
OL,18,FJo has also said warnings about sewage
OL,19,Fdischarges, usually provided via an
OL,20,Fapp, are also inadequate, both in
OL,21,FExmouth and beyond.
