OL,6,FThese only let swimmers know when
OL,7,Fbeaches may be polluted between May
OL,8,Fand September.
OL,10,F"There are so many water users now,
OL,11,Fnot just swimmers - lots of people use
OL,12,Fthe water. We need to know, and it
OL,13,Fneeds to be made really accessible,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
