OL,3,CSea swimmer to sue South West Water
OL,4,Cfor dumping sewage
OL,6,FFor Jo, it is the principle that she
OL,7,Fis hoping to establish - asking for
OL,8,Fjust #300 in compensation. But she
OL,9,Fhopes that if she is successful, it
OL,10,Fmay set a precedent for more people to
OL,11,Ftake polluting water companies to
OL,12,Fcourt.
OL,14,FJo adds that she hopes her case may
OL,15,Fmake bosses at sww twice before
OL,16,Frewarding their shareholders and their
OL,17,Fmanagers, when she believes much more
OL,18,Finvestment is needed to protect the
OL,19,Fcoast.
